## Usage Patterns

### Showcase

```tsx
() => (
  <>
    <InlineValidationMessage
      message="Not a valid zip code"
      type="warning"
      description="We were expecting 5 or 9 digits."
    />
    <InlineValidationMessage message="Incorrect password" type="error" />
    <InlineValidationMessage
      message="Your password meets all requirements"
      type="success"
    />
    <InlineValidationMessage
      message="Your password is missing some criteria"
      type="invalid"
    />
    <InlineValidationMessage
      message="This is an informational message"
      type="info"
      description="Additional details about this information."
    />
  </>
)
```

